dc_description_s: This data layer represents addresses for Waushara County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Waushara_Addresses_2018.gdb'. [This data set was developed initially automated by the WI Department of Natural Resources. It is updated and on an on-going basis, by Waushara County. The data contained in this file only covers points address information managed by the County.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://data-waushara.opendata.arcgis.com/
